{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"dare-titan-tuple","description":"# S5 — The `gerrit-verify.yaml` workflow (reuse `test.yml`)\n\nPart of epic 1fa8 (CI as a second Gerrit gate vote via gerrit-to-platform → GitHub Actions).\n\n## Why\nThis is the workflow g2p dispatches — it runs the SAME checks as `.github/workflows/test.yml` and\ncasts the `Verified` vote. It follows the fixed 3-job g2p production shape (clear-vote →\nbuild-and-test → vote), keeping checks drift-free by reusing the existing steps.\n\n## What\nAuthor `.github/workflows/gerrit-verify.yaml` with `workflow_dispatch` + the nine `GERRIT_*`\ninputs and the three jobs, all third-party actions SHA-pinned.\n\n## Scope\n- `.github/workflows/gerrit-verify.yaml` (and optionally converge with `test.yml`).\n- Depends on S4 (the GitHub vars/secret) and references the `Verified` label from S1.\n- Out of scope: g2p host install (S3), the gate activation (S6).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Author `.github/workflows/gerrit-verify.yaml` triggered by `workflow_dispatch` with the nine\n      `GERRIT_*` inputs; `concurrency` keyed on the change with `cancel-in-progress: true`.\n- [ ] `clear-vote` job: `lfreleng-actions/gerrit-review-action` `vote-type: clear` (resets\n      `Verified→0`; verified semantics) + a short `sleep` for replication.\n- [ ] `build-and-test` job: `lfreleng-actions/checkout-gerrit-change-action` (fetch the exact\n      `GERRIT_REFSPEC`) then the existing `test.yml` steps (lint / typecheck / test matrix + the\n      module-size / prompt-index / criteria-routing gates + coverage floor).\n- [ ] `vote` job (`if: always()`): `im-open/workflow-conclusion` then `gerrit-review-action\n      vote-type: ${{ WORKFLOW_CONCLUSION }}` → `Verified` +1/-1, with the run URL in the vote message.\n- [ ] SHA-pin all third-party actions; decide `test.yml` convergence (recommend the\n      `gerrit-verify-manual-dispatch.yaml` hybrid so one file serves Gerrit dispatch + manual runs).","id":"9b19-5456-58ee-4c09","parent_id":"1fa8-9db4-7c1c-48f3","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"S5 — The gerrit-verify.yaml workflow (reuse test.yml)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782956276675691001,"uuid":"585f61f8-854c-4c05-b600-fa7390049981"}